# Software Requirements Specification (srs) 

*Project Description

## Requirements

-Req. 1.0 
The Back Enhanced PDFBOX System (BEPS) shall provide a mechanism for users to annotate existing PDF documents with text.
-Req 1.1
In annotations composed of text, the user shall be able to specify the font of each glyph in the text from a set of at least two different fonts.
-Req 1.1.1
The BEPS shall include at least two different user selectable fonts.
-Req 2.0 
The BEPS shall provide users with a mechanism to highlight existing text in PDF documents
-Req 3.0
A GUI shall be implemented to allow users to draw lines on the document


Note: 1.1 and 1.1.1 are basically duplicates
